DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY

Title:
AoM Publications, 2010-2018
Repository:
Kheel Center for Labor-Management Documentation & Archives
Collection Number:
5289 PUBS
Abstract:
This collection consists of the publications of the Academy of Management in paper form. For publications in digital form see collection 5289 PUBS(d). The Kheel Center continues to receive all current AoM publications, which are added to this collection.
Creator:
Academy of Management (AoM)
Quanitities:
58.28 cubic feet
Language:
Collection material in English
Processing Information

In March 2019 the container list for this collection was rearranged by Academy of Management Divison and thereunder publication title, then date.
Access to the collections in the Kheel Center is restricted. Please contact a reference archivist for access to these materials.
Conditions Governing Use

This collection must be used in keeping with the Kheel Center Information Sheet and Procedures for Document Use.
INFORMATION FOR USERS
Preferred Citation

AoM Publications #5289 PUBS. Kheel Center for Labor-Management Documentation and Archives, Cornell University Library.
Related Materials

Burgess "Status of Women in Academy of Management" Memoir 5904m: Paul Gordon Collection of Academy of Management Miscellany 5920 AV: AoM Audio-Visual Collection 5977 mf: AoM Additional copy of publications on Microfilm 6012: Charles D. Wrege Papers 6019: AoM Eastern Academy of Management Records 6134: AoM Publications Additional Publications 6278: David Van Fleet Collection of Academy of Management Records
